Title: Misunderstood.
Body (HTML):
Rooting for the good guys is boring. 😈

In collaboration with Disney and their infamous villains, we’re bringing you the palette to rule them all, Misunderstood. This mixed finish 15 pan eyeshadow palette combines intense mattes, colour shifting duochromes, and rich metallics.

Scheme all the ways you’ll slay your look, it won’t be hard with this palette.

This item is limited edition.

©Disney
